Package gym

Class Date

java.lang.Object
gym.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
Initializes and creates Date objects for use within other classes. Dates involve a member's date of birth and expiration date. Date class checks validity of given date and compares dates to other dates.
Author:
Reiya Dave, Ifrah Sajjad
